Head to the State Library of NSW’s rooftop bar for trivia on the first Wednesday of every month. 

The Library Bar is an open-air drinks spot with unique views of the Harbour and Sydney skyline from the top of Australia’s oldest Library.&nbsp;

Test your bookish smarts on literary conundrums and general knowledge, along with the State Library's collections and exhibitions.

