The popular Cuburra Beach Festival returns after its sold-out success in 2024. 

There will be 20 original bands, playing on the Crookhaven Park Oval. Plus&nbsp;free live music at selected cafes on the Cafe Trail and on Sunday the&nbsp;Boomers Bash with throw back to the hits of the 70's at the Community Centre. &nbsp;

On Saturday morning at Crookhaven Oval look forward to free community entertainment, with face painting and circus school for the kids plus delicious food stalls and a buzzing market with lots of local goodies for sale.
